        "Output_template": "{\"name\":\"{reference}.pdf\",\"remove_margins\":\"\",\"setPaperType\":\"a4\",\"content\":\"<style type=\\\"text/css\\\">body {\\n        font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\n      }\\n      table {\\n        border-collapse: collapse;      /*this gets rid of the double border in the table*/\\n      }\\n       table, th, td {        /*This styling applies to all the tables*/\\n        font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\n        border: 1px solid black;\\n        margin-left:50px;\\n        padding-left:5px;\\n        page-break-inside:avoid;     /*this makes sure that the table is kept together if the page breaks*/\\n      } \\n      table.PCCfieldsT {       /*This is the main table*/\\n        width: 85%\\n      }\\n      .PCCfieldsT tr td:nth-child(1) {    /*This styling is for the column on the left*/\\n        font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\n        text-align: left;\\n        width: 30%;\\n        font-weight:bold;\\n        vertical-align:top;       /*The element is aligned with the top of the tallest element on the line*/\\n        padding: 5px 5px;        /* top/botom right/left */\\n      }\\n      .PCCfieldsT tr td :nth-child(2) {    /*This styling is for the column on the right*/\\n        font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\n        width: 70%;\\n        padding: 5px 5px;\\n      }\\n      table.formName {         /*This is the table for the form name, ref number and date, which is half of the standard table*/\\n        width: 40%;\\n        margin-top:100px;\\n        margin-right:50px;\\n        text-align: left;\\n      }\\n      .formName tr  td:nth-child(1) {    /*This styling is for the column on the left*/\\n        font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\n        font-size:15px;\\n        text-align: left;\\n        width: 30%;\\n        vertical-align:top;\\n        padding: 5px 5px;        /* top/botom right/left */\\n      }\\n      .formName tr td :nth-child(2) {    /*This styling is for the column on the right*/\\n        width: 70%;\\n        padding: 5px 5px;\\n        text-align: left;\\n      }\\n      .tabName {         /*This is the class for the tab name*/\\n        text-align: left;\\n        margin:60px 0px 10px 50px; /* top right bottom left */\\n      }\\n      .pccSection {\\n        page-break-inside:avoid;  \\n      }\\n      .pccTextArea {\\n        margin:60px 0px 10px 50px; /* top right bottom left */\\n      }\\n</style>\\n<div style=\\\"position: absolute; margin-top: 10px; margin-right:70px;top: 0; right: 20px; width: 90mm; height: 45mm; text-align: right;\\\"><img height=\\\"65\\\" src=\\\"https://fs-filestore-eu.s3.amazonaws.com/portsmouth/branding/images/logo-print.png\\\" width=\\\"221\\\" /></div>\\n\\n<div>\\n<table class=\\\"formName\\\">\\n\\t<tbody>\\n\\t\\t<tr>\\n\\t\\t\\t<th>Form name</th>\\n\\t\\t\\t<td>{form_name}</td>\\n\\t\\t</tr>\\n\\t\\t<tr>\\n\\t\\t\\t<th>Reference</th>\\n\\t\\t\\t<td>{reference}</td>\\n\\t\\t</tr>\\n\\t\\t<tr>\\n\\t\\t\\t<th>Date</th>\\n\\t\\t\\t<td>{today_en}</td>\\n\\t\\t</tr>\\n\\t</tbody>\\n</table>\\n</div>\\n\\n<div class=\\\"pccSection\\\">\\n<h3 class=\\\"tabName\\\">Introduction</h3>\\n\\n<div class=\\\"pccTextArea\\\">\\n<p>Portsmouth City Council Trading Standards, like others services across the country have received some reports of businesses behaving unfairly during the current Corona crisis. These reports generally relate to the sale of household essentials such as cleaning products, and toilet roll. They broadly include claims:</p>\\n\\n<ol>\\n\\t<li>the trader has requested a higher price at the 'point of sale' to that displayed.</li>\\n\\t<li>the trader has vastly inflated the prices (price gouging)</li>\\n\\t<li>traders are selling products that make unsubstantiated health claims relating to the virus.</li>\\n</ol>\\n&nbsp;\\n\\n<p>Portsmouth City Council's Trading Standard's service would like to hear from anyone who has experienced such practices utilising the form below. The information you provide will help us develop our understanding of potential issues arising in connection with the Coronavirus outbreak. Information may also be used to help us in considering or taking enforcement action, should that be appropriate.</p>\\n{#GDPRv2}</div>\\n\\n<div class=\\\"pccSection\\\">\\n<h3 class=\\\"tabName\\\">Business Details</h3>\\n\\n<table class=\\\"PCCfieldsT\\\">\\n\\t<tbody>\\n\\t\\t<tr>\\n\\t\\t\\t<td>What is the name of the business</td>\\n\\t\\t\\t<td>{businessName}</td>\\n\\t\\t</tr>\\n\\t\\t<tr>\\n\\t\\t\\t<td>Where is the business you are reporting based?</td>\\n\\t\\t\\t<td>{whereBusiness}</td>\\n\\t\\t</tr>\\n\\t</tbody>\\n</table>\\n</div>\\n\\n<div>@af:if({whereBusiness} = 'Online')</div>\\n\\n<table class=\\\"PCCfieldsT\\\">\\n\\t<tbody>\\n\\t\\t<tr>\\n\\t\\t\\t<td>What is the URL (web site)?</td>\\n\\t\\t\\t<td>{URL}</td>\\n\\t\\t</tr>\\n\\t</tbody>\\n</table>\\n\\n<div>@endaf:if</div>\\n\\n<div>@af:if({whereBusiness} = 'Portsmouth')</div>\\n\\n<div class=\\\"pccSection\\\">\\n<h3 class=\\\"tabName\\\">Business Address (if known)</h3>\\n\\n<div>@endaf:if</div>\\n\\n<div>{#businessAddress/SF_Sum}</div>\\n\\n<table class=\\\"PCCfieldsT\\\">\\n\\t<tbody>\\n\\t\\t<tr>\\n\\t\\t\\t<td>Business email address (if known)</td>\\n\\t\\t\\t<td>{businessEmail}</td>\\n\\t\\t</tr>\\n\\t\\t<tr>\\n\\t\\t\\t<td>What sector does the business you are reporting operate within?</td>\\n\\t\\t\\t<td>{businessSector}</td>\\n\\t\\t</tr>\\n\\t</tbody>\\n</table>\\n</div>\\n\\n<div class=\\\"pccSection\\\">\\n<h3 class=\\\"tabName\\\">About issue</h3>\\n\\n<table class=\\\"PCCfieldsT\\\">\\n\\t<tbody>\\n\\t\\t<tr>\\n\\t\\t\\t<td>What do you want to report?</td>\\n\\t\\t\\t<td>{reportWhat}</td>\\n\\t\\t</tr>\\n\\t\\t<tr>\\n\\t\\t\\t<td>What is the product in question?</td>\\n\\t\\t\\t<td>{whatIsTheProduct}</td>\\n\\t\\t</tr>\\n\\t\\t<tr>\\n\\t\\t\\t<td>Please provide a description of the issue</td>\\n\\t\\t\\t<td>{#issueDescription}</td>\\n\\t\\t</tr>\\n\\t\\t<tr>\\n\\t\\t\\t<td>Do you have evidence or supporting documents for this issue?</td>\\n\\t\\t\\t<td>{HaveEvidence}</td>\\n\\t\\t</tr>\\n\\t</tbody>\\n</table>\\n</div>\\n\\n<div class=\\\"pccSection\\\">\\n<h3 class=\\\"tabName\\\">Submit</h3>\\n\\n<div class=\\\"pccTextArea\\\">\\n<p>If you would be happy for us to get in touch to follow up on your answers, or ask for more information, please share your contact details below</p>\\n</div>\\n</div>\\n\\n<div class=\\\"pccSection\\\">\\n<h3 class=\\\"tabName\\\">Your details</h3>\\n\\n<div>{#yourDetails/SF_Sum}</div>\\n</div>\"}",
